    <stitle>AFC G-06907R1 - New Design Engine Block Heater to Eliminate Coolant Leakage in International&#174; DT 570
        Engines in certain 4000, 7000, 8000 HPV Models Built Between April 7, 2004 and July 19, 2006
    </stitle>
    <afc id="afc06907">
