        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>
                    <emph type="bold">REVISION DESCRIPTION</emph>
                </para>
                <para>
                    <emph type="italic">Suspect population build date range changed from 4/2/2004 thru 5/8/2006 to
                        4/7/2004 thru 7/19/2006. All vehicles were properly marked in ISIS, only the dates in this
                        service procedure were incorrect.
                    </emph>
                </para>
                <para>The new design engine block heater has improved mounting torque retention and seals to better
                    withstand engine operating temperature.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
